24/03/2010
BELGRADE, Serbia -- The justice ministry requested on Tuesday (March 23rd) that Greece extradite Simeon Vilovski, a close associate of Bishop Artemije. Vilovski was arrested on March 11th in Thessaloniki, based on an arrest warrant issued by Serbia. The cleric is suspected of embezzling 350,000 euros intended for the reconstruction of monasteries in Kosovo. (Tanjug, B92, RTS - 23/03/10)
